{"type":"message","id":"629d12e3","parentId":"3833591b","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:01:33.985Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vrmsclkch7ui_3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-19\n\n## Context Monitor\n- 15:45 - Context usage at 67% (133,611/200,000 tokens), exceeds 60% threshold\n  - Not yet at 85% auto-trigger, but approaching\n- 19:00 - Context usage at 76% (151,703/200,000 tokens), ⚠️ climbing toward 85% auto-trigger threshold\n\n## Notes\n- 下午好，Sir\n\n## Context Trend\n- 15:45 - 67% (133,611 tokens)\n- 19:00 - 76% (151,703 tokens)\n- 19:35 - 78% (156,819 tokens) ⚠️ approaching 85% auto-trigger threshold\n  - ~13,181 tokens remaining before 85% threshold (170,000)\n  - Suggestion: Sir may want to start a fresh session soon to reset context\n- 20:35 - 21% (41k/200k tokens) ✅ Context reset/compacted - healthy level\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773932493983}}
